WEBVTT

00:00:00.000 --> 00:00:01.700
You know what? I'll say it.

00:00:02.400 --> 00:00:07.900
If we move forward without the security patch, we're accepting a known risk.

00:00:08.380 --> 00:00:10.340
Priya, you always have a problem.

00:00:10.660 --> 00:00:12.760
We do not have time to refactor.

00:00:13.160 --> 00:00:15.260
I say let's just push forward.

00:00:15.880 --> 00:00:17.140
I agree with Elena.
